<div id="pf4470" class="pf w4d h2fe" data-page-no="4470"><div class="pc pc4470 w4d h2fe"><div class="t m57a x92 h5 y2f16 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSON 9 August 26 to September 1 </div><div class="t m8b x71 h5 y4d1 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Be glad then, ye children of Zion, </div><div class="t m4d6 x15 h5 y4a ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and rejoice in the Lord your God: for </div><div class="t m7cd x27 h5 y8cc ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">he hath given you the former rain </div><div class="t m116b x27 h5 y3ec ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">moderately, and he will cause to come </div><div class="t m580 x27 h5 y5e0 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">down for you the rain, the former rain, </div><div class="t maf x27 h5 y22a ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and the latter rain in the first month&quot; </div><div class="t m689 x27 h5 yae6 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Joel 2:23). </div><div class="t m3a0 x26 h35 y1b6 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">This verse had a historic immediate </div><div class="t m3aa x27 h35 y211 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">application. God promised to restore </div><div class="t mde8 x27 h35 y8c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the normal rainfall for the different </div><div class="t m753 x27 h35 y3ef ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">seasons, since this regularity of the </div><div class="t m20a x27 h35 y402 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">rain was the basis for good crops and </div><div class="t m4b3 x27 h35 y287 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">abundance of food. The early or </div><div class="t mb61 x27 h35 y848 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">former rain used to come in the </div><div class="t m80 x27 h35 y1d5 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">autumn of the northern hemisphere, </div><div class="t me62 x27 h35 y90 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and it was very appropriate to produce </div><div class="t m81e x27 h35 y365 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the germination, because it was the </div><div class="t m892 x27 h35 y34e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">sowing time. The latter rain usually </div><div class="t m286 x27 h35 y5ed ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">came in spring to ripen the grain and </div><div class="t m5f4 x27 h35 y60 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to bring the crop to maturity. </div><div class="t m74b x18 h35 ya27 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">But this &apos;promise was preserved </div><div class="t m61a x27 h35 y41d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">because of its important spiritual and </div><div class="t m6c7 x27 h35 y31e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">prophetic application. &quot;The Lord </div><div class="t m51 x27 h35 y657 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">employs these operations of nature to </div><div class="t m1581 x27 h35 y58a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">represent the work of the Holy Spirit. </div><div class="t m58a x27 h35 y84b ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">As the dew and the rain are given first </div><div class="t m5ea x27 h35 y321 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to cause the seed to germinate, and </div><div class="t m120 x27 h35 yba0 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">then to ripen the harvest, so the Holy </div><div class="t m587 x27 h35 y8a8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Spirit is given to carry forward, from </div><div class="t m8d9 x27 h35 ycf9 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">one stage to another, the process of </div><div class="t m4b3 x27 h35 y254 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">spiritual </div><div class="t m425 x5b h35 y254 ff5 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">growth.&quot;â€”Testimonies to </div><div class="t m41e x27 h35 y5f0 ff5 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Ministers, </div><div class="t m80c x49 h35 y456 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">p. 506. </div><div class="t m149 x18 h35 y773 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">This promise applies not only to the </div><div class="t m168 x11 h35 y7b ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">individual life of the Christian, but also </div><div class="t ma7a x11 h35 y457 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to the history of the church at large. </div><div class="t m4b5 x27 h35 y80 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Hebrew word translated &quot;rain&quot; </div><div class="t m3c7 x11 h35 yc48 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">means also a violent shower, or a real </div><div class="t m3c5 x11 h35 y972 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">downpour. This suggests that rain can </div><div class="t mdd2 x11 h35 y27a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">be torrential as well as gentle! </div><div class="t ma8c x18 h35 y1096 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Applied to the church in general, </div><div class="t mbd8 x11 h35 y14ae ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the early rain represents the  </div><div class="t mbbb x70 h35 y18f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">outpouring of the Holy Spirit on the </div><div class="t m32d x70 h35 y347 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Day of Pentecost and during the rest of </div><div class="t m9ea x70 h35 y1b2 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the apostolic era, while the latter rain </div><div class="t m7a0 x70 h35 y2fb ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">refers to the powerful manifestation of </div><div class="t mb66 x70 h35 y2b2 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the Holy Spirit that is going to usher in </div><div class="t m699 x70 h35 y50 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the last stages of the history of the </div><div class="t mb6e x70 h35 y376 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">church that will see the finishing of </div><div class="t mb61 x70 h35 y1868 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God&apos;s work in the earth. </div><div class="t m119c xab h35 y1b7 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">In this lesson we shall consider the </div><div class="t m7a4 x70 h35 yd9 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">former and the latter rains as </div><div class="t m2ae x70 h35 y500 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">individual spiritual experiences as well </div><div class="t m224 x70 h35 y654 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">as phases in the history of the church. </div><div class="t m2b2 xab h35 yc46 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">We shall study some of the </div><div class="t m2ce x70 h35 y248 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">wonderful promises God has given </div><div class="t m782 x70 h35 y848 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">concerning the outpouring of His Holy </div><div class="t m1317 x70 h35 y9 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Spirit on the church and His purpose </div><div class="t m105d x70 h35 y156 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">in doing so. We are also going to </div><div class="t m825 x70 h35 y365 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">consider the importance of this </div><div class="t mbba x70 h35 y134c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">power, the willingness of God to </div><div class="t m336 x70 h35 y498 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">bestow this gift, and the reasons why </div><div class="t m9b5 x70 h35 y61 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">this gift has not yet been fully </div><div class="t m813 x70 h35 y109 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">received. </div><div class="t m5fd x70 h5 y26c ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">DAILY HIGHLIGHTS </div><div class="t m23f x70 h5 y352 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t m1f2 x7b h5 y9d2 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Historic Early Rain </div><div class="t m14c1 x7b h5 y40b ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Acts 2:1-4) </div><div class="t m558 x70 h5 y2c3 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m7d7 x7b h5 y2c3 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Promises of the Latter Rain </div><div class="t m774 x7b h5 ye9 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Joel 2:23) </div><div class="t mb7 x70 h5 y5da ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t mcf9 x7b h5 y5da ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Purpose of the Latter Rain </div><div class="t m156 x7b h5 y293 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Rev. 18:1, 4) </div><div class="t m1ce x70 h5 ycf9 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t m88 x7b h5 y9a ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Importance of the Latter Rain </div><div class="t m1d3 x7b h5 y490 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Zech. 10:1) </div><div class="t m8a8 x70 h5 y221 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5. </div><div class="t m9c1 x7b h5 y221 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Reason for Delay </div><div class="t m749 x22 h5 y1e2 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(2 Chron. 7:14) </div><div class="t m2ef x56 h5 y7a ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">6. </div><div class="t mb52 x7b h5 y7a ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Early and Latter Rain Experience </div><div class="t m3bc x22 h5 y506 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Mark 4:28) </div></div><div class="